      <title>港股录得2018年以来最长连涨纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/hong-kong-stocks-are-on-their-longest-winning-streak-since-2018</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港股市正处于 2018 年以来最长的连续上涨势头，这进一步表明去年表现最差的市场之一正在顺利复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/hong-kong-stocks-are-on-their-longest-winning-streak-since-2018</guid>
