    <item>
      <title>利率前景看好金价将迎来自二月份以来最差的单周走势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/gold-heads-for-worst-weekly-run-since-february-on-rate-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心通胀风险持续存在，美联储可能需要比之前预期更长的时间降息，金价出现两个多月来首次连续一周下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/gold-heads-for-worst-weekly-run-since-february-on-rate-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 01:39:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>麦格理利润下降 32%，低于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-03/macquarie-profit-falls-32-missing-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[麦格理集团公布的收益低于分析师的平均预期。截至 3 月 31 日的一年中，这家澳大利亚投资银行和资产管理公司的净收入下降 32% 至 35.2 亿澳元（23.1 亿美元）。保罗·艾伦在彭博电视台报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-03/macquarie-profit-falls-32-missing-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 01:20:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
